Dangerous delusions: biomass is not a renewable energy source
       Using trees and crops is being touted by the biomass industry as a
       way to curb carbon emissions, but it turns out bioenergy and
       biofuel industries are as bad as fossil fuels for the climate, the
       environment and local communities.
